first elected in 1978 he was defeated in 1980 but was elected 
again in 1982 1984 and 1986 the first year the governorship was 
made a fouryear term 
the republican gubernatorial race pits us rep tommy robinson 
a former police chief and sheriff against sheffield nelson a 
former utility executive 
