care act raise the salaries of members of congress and severely 
restrict abortions 
but mazzolis decision not to accept pacs may be his downfall 
as of may 18 mazzoli said he had raised 133370 from individual 
contributors hutter had raised 172550 by may 9 including 
40000 from pacs 
mazzoli 57 decided in december to set an example by becoming 
