a marching band and the cheers of thousands 
of residents created a rousing homecoming today for frank reed who 
spent 3 years as a hostage in lebanon 
the noontime procession officially welcomed reed back to this 
suburb just north of boston where residents never lost hope during 
his 44 months of captivity 
reed and his family led the citys high school band through 
