government had passed the report on to tehran bush at a news 
conference on may 3 promised to provide the information as a 
gesture of goodwill 
we have made a major effort of collecting information 
fitzwater said essentially the conclusions are the same the 
four individuals they are concerned with are dead 
the four iranians two diplomats a journalist and a driver 
disappeared from beirut during the 1982 israeli invasion of 
lebanon iran in the past has suggested lebanese christian 
militiamen had a role in the abductions 
