circumstances of the killings or on the identity of the 
perpetrators the contents of the report were not disclosed 
he said that the united states conferred with the international 
red cross other countries and a lot of private sources that we 
developed in compiling its report to iran 
at his may 3 news conference bush said he hoped providing iran 
with information on the fate of the four missing iranians would 
