divided over slavery to proclaim in sovereign love god created 
the world good and makes everyone equally in gods image male and 
female of every race and people to live as one community 
if approved the statement will be sent to the churchs 171 
presbyteries if twothirds of the regional bodies approve the 
statement it will come before the 1991 general assembly for a 
final review and vote 
among other issues 
in a document titled restoring creation for ecology and 
justice the committee on social witness policy recommends the 
