spokesman gennady gerasimov after hearing of yeltsins victory 
president mikhail s gorbachev has his critics from both the 
left and the right and possibly it is better to have the election 
of a critic from the left he said 
gerasimov and other soviet officials were at the united nations 
to brief reporters before the ussoviet summit on wednesday in 
washington 
