the soviets have an interest in positioning the asian part of 
their country as a pacific rim player said carol piasente 
spokeswoman for the chamber of commerce the purpose of this 
luncheon is to build a relationship between the west coast 
companies and the far eastern part of the soviet union 
in addition to hewlettpackard other companies with 
