explosion that could result in the release of plutonium the 
experts have been using computer studies to see if their fears have 
foundation the report said but so far their studies have found 
no firm basis for such a possible accident 
the report said the concern lies in the design of the missile 
which has threestages the missile contains its most explosive 
rocket fuel in a cylinder at the center of its uppermost stage and 
the fuel is surrounded by eight thermonuclear warheads 
