advertisers since january nearly all of the buyers so far have 
been european 
pravda the official newspaper of the soviet communist party 
sent out notices to dozens of american companies encouraging them 
to buy fullpage ads during the summit it claims circulation of 
more than 8 million 
</TEXT>
