<TEXT>
about 30 people marched outside the pittsburgh 
press on may 19 accusing the news media of bias in covering 
abortion issues 
some of the marchers said they objected to the use of 
proabortion vocabulary in news stories 
that is the vocabulary that calls us antiabortion and calls 
