<TEXT>
in the world of tutus and toe shoes red is 
particularly hot this season barely a week seems to pass without a 
mention of some dance companys financial woes 
the problems arent particularly new to nonprofit organizations 
everybodys always been struggling said stephanie french 
vice president for corporate contributions and cultural affairs at 
