radio 
a radio listener is someone who has to produce the images in 
his mind in his head whoevers listening is responsible for 50 
percent of the input of whatever hes listening to 
mairowitz like warner also received a giles cooper award this 
year for the stalin sonata about a female pianist imprisoned 
during stalins 1937 purges 
