claimed retail sales of 650 million a studio typically enjoys 10 
percent of the wholesale revenues generated by the merchandise to 
which it holds the copyrights 
in 1980 licensed products had retail sales of 99 billion by 
1989 that figure had surged to 646 billion about 3 billion 
worth of merchandise inspired by movies and television programs was 
sold last year 
