<TEXT>
schooled since birth in the discipline of the 
theater amy irving sought interviews to promote her new movie only 
days before delivering her second child 
she already was the mother of one of the most famous and 
richest boys in the world max spielberg whose father is her 
former husband film tycoon steven spielberg irving and spielberg 
were divorced last year 
max now has a halfbrother gabriel davis baretto born may 4 to 
amy and bruno baretto director of her new film max also has 
another halfsibling since spielberg and kate capshaw became the 
parents of a daughter sasha on may 14 but thats a different 
story 
like spielbergcapshaw barettoirving are not married but we 
plan to be declares irving 
her new movie is a paramount pictures release a show of 
force based on anne nelsons book murder under two flags it 
delves into the political intrigue surrounding the murder of two 
young men in 1978 in puerto rico the alleged coverup caused a 
government scandal that apparently still has reverberations 
the script is very close to the facts of the case irving 
said there was some license that we took in telling the story 
and there were some demands that we do not use real names there 
were rumors that the american government is trying not to expose 
this film too much because it does come down pretty heavily on them 
the fact that the two boys were set up to look like 
cubanbacked terrorists and then murdered in cold blood has been 
proven how high up the influence goes and who was involved is 
still under investigation 
the actress admitted her own ignorance of puerto rico before 
making the film i even asked what currency they used her 
stay there provided an education and she concludes with 
understatement i dont think that the situation there is one 
that america has helped 
like many of todays film heroines irving plays a television 
reporter a widow with two children her investigation puts her 
life in jeopardy puts her familys life in jeopardy and makes her 
question her own vision of what america was she seeks the truth 
and comes into her own strength in seeking the truth 
her role as kate ryan de melendez is the mainstay of the plot 
which also involves andy garcia as the prosecutor lou diamond 
phillips as an undercover agent and robert duvall as the television 
station manager also in the cast is irvings mother priscilla 
pointer 
with an actress mother and a father who was a distinguished 
stage director amy irving grew up in the theater the late jules 
irving was artistic director of san franciscos american repertory 
theater when amy was born in palo alto calif 37 years ago she 
made her stage debut at 9 months in rumplestiltskin trained at 
her fathers theater and later at the london academy of music and 
dramatic art 
over the years irving has divided her time between stage 
amadeus heartbreak house and screen carrie 
yentl crossing delancey daughter of one director and 
former wife of another it seemed inevitable she would fall under 
the spell of her a show of force director 
i met bruno before the film she related he flew up from 
brazil about a year ago march and we talked about the film i had 
seen his dona flora and her two husbands and he showed me other 
of his brazilian films he has made nine there all of his films 
have a central character of a very strong woman a woman who 
travels through some kind of journey in life in each one the 
performances were so impressive that i couldnt wait to be directed 
by him 
we had a wonderful experience making the film and afterward 
more happened it turned out to be a grand experience in my life 
after their marriage she says they plan to make their home 
here she also has a house in new mexico and he will keep his base 
in brazil 
a show of force is brunos first englishlanguage film and 
he plans to come to america and pursue his career here irving 
said he got tired of people reading his films all his films 
are subtitled outside brazil and portugal to be able to have 
people watch the faces as the story unfolds is something that hes 
wanted for a long time 
well go to brazil weve spent some time there and im 
learning portuguese his 13yearold daughter lives with us and 
our life is pretty international now max has already learned how 
to ask for a chocolate cookie in portuguese 
